    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally sound with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed. Mechanical upkeep is current, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and recent valve shim adjustments to ensure precise timing and valvetrain harmonics. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, maintaining factory-spec kinematics. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
